nodes.text: Freddie Prinze Jr. (born March 8, 1976) is an American actor. He voiced the Jedi character Kanan Jarrus in the animated series Star Wars Rebels, which aired on Disney XD, and the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker.
His wife, Sarah Michelle Gellar, appeared on the Rebels show with him for the second season, portraying the Seventh Sister.
